title: Navigate forwards to a collapsed disclosure button
instructions: With focus on the 'Navigate forwards from here' link, navigate to the 'About' disclosure button.
assertions: roleNavigation nameMythicalUniversity roleList listSetSize3 roleButton nameAbout stateCollapsed

title: Navigate backwards to a collapsed disclosure button
instructions: With focus on the 'Navigate backwards from here' link, navigate to the 'Academics' disclosure button.
assertions: roleNavigation nameMythicalUniversity roleList listSetSize3 roleButton nameAcademics stateCollapsed

title: Navigate forwards to an expanded disclosure button
instructions: With focus on the 'Navigate forwards from here' link, navigate to the 'About' disclosure button.
assertions: roleNavigation nameMythicalUniversity roleList listSetSize3 roleButton nameAbout stateExpanded

title: Navigate backwards to an expanded disclosure button
instructions: With focus on the 'Navigate backwards from here' link, navigate to the 'Academics' disclosure button.
assertions: roleNavigation nameMythicalUniversity roleList listSetSize3 roleButton nameAcademics stateExpanded

title: Navigate to the next collapsed disclosure button
instructions: With focus on the 'Admissions' disclosure button, navigate to the 'Academics' disclosure button.

title: Navigate to the previous collapsed disclosure button
instructions: With focus on the 'Admissions' disclosure button, navigate to the 'About' disclosure button.

title: Navigate to the next expanded disclosure button
instructions: With focus on the 'Admissions' disclosure button, navigate to the 'Academics' disclosure button.

title: Navigate to the previous expanded disclosure button
instructions: With focus on the 'Admissions' disclosure button, navigate to the 'About' disclosure button.

title: Navigate to the first collapsed disclosure button
instructions: With focus on the 'Admissions' disclosure button, navigate to the 'About' disclosure button.

title: Navigate to the last collapsed disclosure button
instructions: With focus on the 'Admissions' disclosure button, navigate to the 'Academics' disclosure button.

title: Navigate to the first expanded disclosure button
instructions: With focus on the 'Admissions' disclosure button, navigate to the 'About' disclosure button.

title: Navigate to the last expanded disclosure button
instructions: With focus on the 'Admissions' disclosure button, navigate to the 'Academics' disclosure button.

title: Request information about a collapsed disclosure button
instructions: With focus on the 'About' disclosure button, read information about the disclosure button.

title: Request information about an expanded disclosure button
instructions: With focus on the 'About' disclosure button, read information about the disclosure button.

title: Activate a collapsed disclosure button
instructions: With focus on the 'About' disclosure button, change its state to 'expanded'.

title: Activate an expanded disclosure button
instructions: With focus on the 'About' disclosure button, change its state to 'collapsed'.

title: Navigate to a link in the open dropdown from its associated disclosure button
instructions: With focus on the 'About' disclosure button, navigate to the 'Overview' link.

title: Navigate to the current page link from an expanded disclosure button
instructions: With focus on the 'About' disclosure button, navigate to the 'Overview' link.

title: Navigate to an expanded disclosure button from a link in its associated dropdown
instructions: With focus on the 'Overview' link, navigate to the 'About' disclosure button.

title: Navigate to a link in a dropdown from a collapsed disclosure button
instructions: With focus on the 'Admissions' disclosure button, navigate to the 'Campus Tours' link.

title: Navigate to a collapsed disclosure button from the last link in a dropdown
instructions: With focus on the 'Campus Tours' link, navigate to the 'Admissions' disclosure button.

title: Dismiss a dropdown
instructions: With focus on the 'Overview' link, close the dropdown.

title: Activate a link in a dropdown
instructions: With focus on the 'Overview' link, activate the link.
